    <item>
      <title>Rachel Reeves 如何决定英国需要大力投资经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/how-rachel-reeves-decided-uk-needs-to-bet-big-on-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[10月30日，英国政府公布预算案后不久，在经济信心暴跌和企业抗议增税的情况下，压力重重的雷切尔·里夫斯向财政部官员传达了一条关键信息：“我们需要在增长方面走得更远、更快。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/how-rachel-reeves-decided-uk-needs-to-bet-big-on-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法兰克福天际线因旧办公楼空置而变暗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/frankfurt-s-skyline-darkens-as-old-office-buildings-sit-vacant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法兰克福最中心的街区之一，距离城市主要火车站只有几步之遥，一栋 19 层的高楼曾是德国中央合作银行联合投资部门的办公场所，现已空置四年多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/frankfurt-s-skyline-darkens-as-old-office-buildings-sit-vacant</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受房地产市场低迷影响 中国未能实现财政支出目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/china-misses-fiscal-spending-target-on-effects-of-housing-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于房地产市场低迷导致地方政府资金紧张且无法履行资金承诺，中国政府去年未能实现支出目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/china-misses-fiscal-spending-target-on-effects-of-housing-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 02:51:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
