      <title>墨西哥央行将考虑在 2025 年初大幅降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/mexico-central-bank-will-consider-larger-rate-cuts-early-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥央行委员会在一份报告中表示，由于通胀放缓，墨西哥央行可能在今年首次货币政策会议上大幅下调基准利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/mexico-central-bank-will-consider-larger-rate-cuts-early-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 02:16:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Japfa 家族提出将新加坡家禽公司私有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/japfa-family-makes-offer-to-take-singapore-poultry-firm-private</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佳发有限公司 (Japfa Ltd.) 已故创始人的家人提出将这家新加坡肉类生产商私有化，对该公司的估值为 11.8 亿新元（8.77 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/japfa-family-makes-offer-to-take-singapore-poultry-firm-private</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 01:43:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
